{"tid":1776531,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［警世］唔好再浪費時間同陳雲／熱狗糾纏落去，有時候無視佢地更著數","createTime":"2019-12-09T15:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T09:27:43.000Z","uid":39021,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8b320c9f8a145b09cb813f4ad7fc3f3f255d594a","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:06:44.000Z","msg":"有時候陳雲既文章其實幾實用，或者學大家講句，「食咗藥」<br />\n一直以黎陳雲同熱狗屌醒大家唔好再迷信泛民，功不可沒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但「食藥」／「未食藥」呢種講法完全係錯</span></strong><br />\n真相係，陳雲同熱狗其實係一個Cult<br />\n佢地唔需要好多人支持，只需要一班超級死忠就夠，有咩論述就靠死忠到處傳開去<br />\n要維持呢班信眾既支持，就要靠一個信念：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眾人皆醉我獨醒</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n到咗最近幾個月，陳雲建議大家轉攻為守，佢地就開始失去帶頭能力<br />\n姑且唔講究竟轉攻為守係唔係一個好既策略（我個人覺得係）<br />\n因為陳雲再比唔到一個確切方向大家，大家就開始唔再點參考佢<br />\n陳雲見到自己人氣下滑，為咗維持支持度，就開展「無食藥」模式<br />\n透過不斷屌泛民落後無用累三家同提出神怪理論，去暗示自己其實仲有招，只不過係泛民破壞緊個局<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">實際上陳雲係完全未諗到任何積極對策，亦即係進入唔到「食藥」模式</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n陳雲同熱狗本質上就係要靠屌泛民為生<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">你同熱狗鬥屌埋啲無謂野，只係玩緊泥漿摔角，浪費時間</span></strong><br />\n陳雲係值得參考，但<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">當你見到佢不斷鳩屌泛民又比唔出實質方向時，其實只要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無視佢地</span>就得</span></strong><br />\n換句話講，佢都只係兄弟爬山緊，想維持下自己人氣，免得有好論述講出黎時會完全無人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d623cb5f40993f649edf8721d1b23c961304899f","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdc16df43a8f819d030a8b3d46e3cd22c8c5608","tid":1776531,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5d40daf6e56093b19b014e91e8608ded5743121","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8603a06d7a01c7f745b1848b11c66ff11a53354","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc14283494efdf41734ff581f87902234b646ba","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a6abe0bf8c6714715678496cabd4c8bdfc5d5f","tid":1776531,"uid":26854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2343e156c2bcaa4fc2b418ee62421431ba142387","tid":1776531,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08f6929e4b3349712c74e8a3f8f6946e114e4b4f","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5e93d01d0d381ccf32682d5afa69a3250a4e66","tid":1776531,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/